OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fmostly dry through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, though it will be mostly
OL,8,Fcloudy, and in the north there could
OL,9,Fbe the odd spot of rain. A mild night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA cloudy and dry morning.
OL,12,FStaying dry in the afternoon with some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells developing
OL,14,Flater. Quite warm and humid.
